&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;MS or equivalent experience in a relevant, quantitative field such as Computer Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Software Engineering, with an emphasis on AI/ML theory and/or practical development. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;5+ years of post-MS industry experience working on developing AI/ML

