&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;The role reports to the Manager of Genomics Late Stage Development. This role will be an onsite role based in our Brisbane, California headquarters.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
