&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;Perform technical troubleshooting, identify and implement process improvements across the lab by thinking critically about the execution of all experiments&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
